#do not run this command around midnight!
LANGS="cze deu eng fra hun ita nor por rom slv spa srp"
cp summary-head.html ../WG1/distantreading.github.io/ELTeC/index.html
for lang in $LANGS; do
    echo "$lang";
    cd ../ELTeC-$lang;
    saxon -xi corpus=$lang  driver.tei ../Scripts/summarize.xsl >> ../WG1/distantreading.github.io/ELTeC/index.html
    cd ../Scripts;
  done
  today=`date --iso`
echo "<p>Last updated on $today</p>" >> ../WG1/distantreading.github.io/ELTeC/index.html
cat summary-tail.html >> ../WG1/distantreading.github.io/ELTeC/index.html